// CSI Ps c  Send Device Attributes (Primary DA).
//     Ps = 0  or omitted -> request attributes from terminal.  The
//     response depends on the decTerminalID resource setting.
//     -> CSI ? 1 ; 2 c  (``VT100 with Advanced Video Option'')
